{"tid":709352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歧視中國人？】司機唔識講英文被圍剿 星洲網民：嚟打工就要學！","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T03:09:40.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8408883cfd0b9ec9e5c2448db4422e6d14a430","tid":709352,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529418535_72d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529418535_72d6.jpg&h=5aca5b19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國人在新加坡打工，不懂說英語被罵已不是第一次發生，當地人認為服務行業應該培訓員工提升英語能力，畢竟工作主要是在前線面對客人。去年，一名巴士司機懷疑2歲和4歲的小孩沒付車費，拒絕繼續開車。但因為司機不會說英文，導致事件僵持着，全車人都受影響，最終還要改乘另一輛巴士。<br />\n<br />\n繼續睇：【歧視中國人？】華女侍應唔識講英文 俾新加坡大叔辱罵：滾回國啦！（ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2tmEBpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2tmEBpg&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=bd82ec60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2tmEBpg</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n當時有網民在facebook貼出巴士司機的相片和經過，並引發激烈討論：「又是外籍人才......」「巴士公司是在做甚麼的？請員工不用學簡單的英文嗎？只會請人也不會教他們多少歲的小孩子不用付費嗎？爛公司，我一看照片那個巴士車長就知道從哪裏來的。」「是中國車長嗎？不懂講簡單英語，車上搭客這麼多為何不隨便找一個繙譯呢？為甚麼要搞到全車人下車？車廠是你爸開的麼，說開就開說不開就停下，還耽誤了乘客的不便。笨蛋！」<br />\n<br />\n新加坡網民認為：「新加坡作為一個英語國家，在這裏出生的人從幼兒園到小學到中學、大學都說英語。英語是這裏的官方語言，在所有種族中廣泛使用，在新加坡，英語是的士司機的必修課。對於前台銷售人員和服務員來說，用英文交流是必備的技能，這樣才能更好的為他人服務。」<br />\n<br />\n另有網民則建議「大食代」加強員工培訓：「Food Republic必須採取行動了，讓他們的員工學習英文，不能讓他們只說普通話，不能只能讓我們理解他們。」另有網民建議如果不會說英文可以去後勤工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180620/58339005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F58339005&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4a54b050\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180620%2F58339005&h=9fd1c030\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180620/58339005</a>"},{"pid":"cd582064d8615cf9d3bfdf4bb848819503002c6d","tid":709352,"uid":26506,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"如果香港廣東話可以達到呢個地位就好"},{"pid":"34379809ef3b1d582f01761be4085c63e4c4063b","tid":709352,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"痴線 唔識講咪當睇唔到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要搞到咁柒既"},{"pid":"faf4f01f18eeb134c3d23255ec4eebecadf8c935","tid":709352,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34379809ef3b1d582f01761be4085c63e4c4063b","tid":709352,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"痴線 唔識講咪當睇唔到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要搞到咁柒既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9281aa92b4595da46ed68c2f07e994972d50689b","tid":709352,"uid":9052,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:59:18.000Z","msg":"去人地地方, 唔識講人地既語言 , 仲要話人地歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2a94bf554109e3085b50620484f6eeeba6456b","tid":709352,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/110051_161b72947116f96067d28af6ff6939ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F110051_161b72947116f96067d28af6ff6939ac.gif&h=d4c57e96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32925a0ccca6b5442338cd0c0ea37308ffc3bd9b","tid":709352,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T03:04:30.000Z","msg":"Get away liao<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" 